<https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28394724/> | Lee et al (2017)        | 20 | Multiple Sclerosis     | 12 mo    | Multimodal Wahls Protocol   | Anxiety (BAI) p=0.001-0.02, depression (BDI) p<0.0001-0.09, cognitive function improved; diet dosage most predictive.
