<https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37772528/> | Ihnatowicz et al (2023) | 28 | Hashimotos Thyroiditis | 12 weeks | Autoimmune Protocol (diet)  | Relative -78% fatigue, -87% depression, many improvements
<https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/35811518/> | Toups et al (2022)      | 25 | Alzheimers/Dementia    | 9 mo     | Precision medicine (diet+)  | MoCA score +3 points (p<0.0001); 80% improved or stable.
<https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/37355891/> | Sandison et al (2023)   | 34 | Alzheimers/Dementia    | 6 mo     | Individualized (diet+)      | MoCA score +3.0 points (p<0.001) in protocol completers.
